  "steps": [
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ひだまりストア・店内売り場――",
      "bg": "images/assets/bg/battle_store_lv1.png",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "すみません。\nこの辺の加湿器って、どれを選べばいいですか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。\nお部屋の広さや使う場所によっておすすめが変わりますよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "ワンルームなんですけど、寝る時に喉が乾く感じがあって。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "それなら、静音タイプがいいかもしれませんね。\n夜、音が気になると使いにくいですし。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "タンク容量も見た方がいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "あ、そうだね。\n寝る前に給水して、朝まで使うなら、少し大きめの方が安心です。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "なるほど……。\nじゃあ、これはどうですか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "それは加湿量が強め。\nワンルームだと、結露が出やすいかもしれない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "そうなんですか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "部屋の換気と置き場所にもよるけど。\n窓際に置くつもりなら、避けた方がいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空、すごい。\nお客様、置く場所は決まっていますか？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "たぶん、窓の近くかなって思ってました。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "なら、こっち。\n加湿量は控えめだけど、湿度センサーがある。\n寝室用なら、その方が使いやすいと思う。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "へえ……。\nこっちの方が値段も少し安いんですね。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "高い方が合うとは限らない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "そうですね。\n使う場所に合っている方が、長く使いやすいと思います。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "じゃあ、これにします。\nありがとうございます。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。\nレジまでお持ちしますね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "あ、お願いします。\nお姉さん、説明すごくわかりやすかったです。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "えっ、ありがとうございます。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "若い客",
      "text": "明るく話してくれるから、聞きやすかったです。\nまた家電で迷ったら聞きに来ますね。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい、ぜひ。\nお待ちしています。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――若い客は美空に案内され、レジの方へ向かっていった。\n夜空は少しだけ売り場に残り、空いた棚の札を直す。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、今の接客、よかったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空がちゃんと説明してたから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "最初に合う商品を絞ったのは夜空だろ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "横から言っただけ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "でも、お客様は助かったと思うぞ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……買ってくれたなら、それでいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空。\n今、少し沈んでないか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "沈んでない。\n沈む理由がない。\nお客様はちゃんと合う商品を選べた。\n美空も褒められた。\nいいことしかないでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "確かに、いいことだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "なら、それでいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "でも、最後に褒められたのは美空だった。\nそれが、少し引っかかった？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "違う。\n美空が褒められるのは嬉しい。\n美空はちゃんと笑える。\n話し方もやわらかい。\nお客様も安心する。\nだから、嬉しい。\n本当に嬉しい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空が、自分に言い聞かせてるように聞こえた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。\n少しだけ、当たってるかもしれない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "今のなし。\n聞こえなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "聞こえたから、忘れない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "忘れて。\n……忘れなくてもいいけど、言わないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "わかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――少しして、美空がレジから戻ってくる。\n嬉しそうな笑顔のまま、夜空の方へ近づいてきた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空、さっきのお客様、すごく喜んでましたよ。\n夜空が選んでくれた商品、ぴったりだったみたい。\n「詳しい人がいて助かった」って言ってました。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……美空に言ってた？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "うん。\nでも、夜空のことだよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空が説明したからでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空が選んだんだよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空が売った。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "二人で売ったんだよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空は、そういうところがまっすぐすぎる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空は考えすぎ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "いいコンビだったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。\n夜空がいてくれると、本当に安心します。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……慣れない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "褒められるのが嫌なのか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "嫌じゃない。\nでも、受け取り方がわからない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "じゃあ、少しずつ受け取ればいいよ。\n夜空に受け取ってほしいから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "さっきの接客、夜空の成果でもある。\nそれは、ちゃんと覚えておいていいと思う。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……店長も簡単に言う。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "簡単には思ってない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……ずるい。\n今日は特に。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
